<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">以青春之名，书写清澈挚爱，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">爱国没有文案，没有理由，只有自豪。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">收下这张爱国福，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">爱国主义精神永记心中</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/2n18Qa8gmEJTowWEWIlkibmyv1mOqJaDxiaqmgUA9wiaznRKG5iczVianDhChkkeicQ3ibv7fyGOuTByeC7D4XLecGy9w/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="99" height="169" style="width: 99px; height: 169px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">讲台上的老师们恪尽职守，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">教给同学们知识，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">收下这张敬业福，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">向每位老师们致敬</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><br/></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>